{"delete":"true","save":"<section class=\"blocks\"><div class=\"blocks__box\"><div class=\"blocks__inner\"><header class=\"blocks__header\"><h2 class=\"blocks__title\">構築済みのEC2にPHP環境をインストールするメモ</h2><div class=\"labels\"><a class=\"labels__link\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"labels__main labels__main--aws\">aws</span></a><a class=\"labels__link\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"labels__sub labels__sub--aws\">EC2</span></a></div></header><section class=\"blocks__text\"><div class=\"blocks__time\"><p>2019.6.29</p><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"time\" value=\"2019.6.29\"></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-0\"><h3 class=\"blocks__title\">まずは、サーバーにSSH!</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-1\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>ssh -i 設定した鍵（パーミッションは400）.pem ec2-user@00.00.00(パブリックIP)</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-2\"><h3 class=\"blocks__description-title\">まずは、yumをupdate</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-3\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>sudo yum update -y</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-4\"><h3 class=\"blocks__description-title\">sudo yum install httpd</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-5\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>sudo service httpd start</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-6\"><h3 class=\"blocks__description-title\">次は、サーバーの言語設定</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-7\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>sudo vim /etc/sysconfig/i18n    ←vimで設定ファイルを開く\r\nLANG=ja_JP.UTF-8   ←vimで設定ファイルをのこの部分を「ja_JP.UTF-8」に修正\r\n</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-8\"><h3 class=\"blocks__description-title\">次は、時刻設定</h3></div><div class=\"b